{"tid":1623373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實記者真係可以多方面多角度撚死班狗","createTime":"2019-10-04T20:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:00:30.000Z","uid":96694,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ae8de249e8af8eeb4eeaaaea6ef1dc2bc0f740f3","tid":1623373,"uid":96694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:25:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5pLw7jmHalQ&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5pLw7jmHalQ%26feature%3Dshare&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=fe4443e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5pLw7jmHalQ&amp;feature=share</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實利君雅第一個point  已經可以釘死班狗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除非決定射擊 <br />\n扳機手指必須放在扳機護環之外</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先其實我好想補充一個好重要既point<br />\n警察係冇口頭上警告既情況下而開槍係有違人權<br />\n呢一點上就已經失左職<br />\n唔好同我講咩情況危急 當時情況唔容許等等<br />\n過往警察開槍射擊任何疑犯、罪犯等<br />\n都有會口頭警告<br />\n而今次開槍既警員係冇任何性命危險既情況下<br />\n而冇作出任何警告係唔係合情合理？<br />\n憑良心講句  冇口頭警告下開槍 仲要射胸口<br />\n同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">謀殺</span></span>有咩分別？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n再講利君雅個point<br />\n咁個隻狗就回應話係屬於 <br />\n「安全防範法」<br />\n目的係令到使用槍械既時候更加安全<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就一直將個焦點放左落 「安全」既問題上<br />\n如果比我係利君雅  <br />\n我就想問  乜手指放在護環之外只係一個安全性既問題？<br />\n係考慮手持槍械既警員射得安唔安全？<br />\n到底其實有冇考慮過當時環境任何人既安全？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">除非決定射擊 <br />\n扳機手指必須放在扳機護環之外</span><br />\n本身就係保障在場既任何人 唔會受到子彈而受傷<br />\n唔係你口中既<br />\n乜野「<span style=\"color: red;\">避免係一個唔想開槍嘅情況下開槍</span>」<ins></ins><br />\n開唔開槍係警員既責任<br />\n警員係有責任保護市民唔會無辜受到子彈所傷害<br />\n一個警員都係人  <br />\n一個人係緊張既情況下 手部受到外來攻擊 <br />\n係有可能唔小心無意之下開左槍<br />\n呢個係人之常情<br />\n所以警員先更加有責任  為左保障市民<br />\n而放隻手指落護環之外<br />\nok?<br />\n<br />\n再講  <br />\n如果一個警員 <br />\n係一個唔想開槍既情況之下 <br />\n放手指落扳機護環之內  <br />\n係有乜野意圖同目的<br />\n你答唔答到我呢個問題？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔想開槍既情況下  <br />\n點解隻手指唔放係扳機護環之外呀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>popo 我屌你老母呀</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ad579d33c3cc2375bd9103e4ecea4852c43f93cc","tid":1623373,"uid":276666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:25:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思  借個位<br />\n<br />\n［新戰術］反蒙面法對反送中運動有利<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623276\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623276</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0f00b2a77683536f3341e77257afaae49fa1edce","tid":1623373,"uid":96694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:26:35.000Z","msg":"其實我真係好想有人可以睇哂成篇文<br />\n希望大家唔好厭我篇文太長 打太多字<br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"76a0299bc4c0339af4e4a7541f4ec3f7286b1429","tid":1623373,"uid":96694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:28:07.000Z","msg":"我知咁夜會冇人睇<br />\n所以我都唔推了<br />\n聽朝訓醒有心機先再推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108f954deb63473f68ce875bbb5d00928e8972e9","tid":1623373,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a82c89395d460305f5012dcbe9219f63ef0005","tid":1623373,"uid":60303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:32:07.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0e929a8455c3e8f020afe8bd81a0878dfe0a3279","tid":1623373,"uid":25699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:34:37.000Z","msg":"依家佢話擺明開槍打你你都吹佢唔脹"},{"pid":"d8d3e63cbe26b377c35017