>\n<br />\n賭神3.3<br />\n#22736<br />\n呢場運動開始玩撚完<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623256</a><br />\n<br />\n生人唔生膽<br />\n#151460<br />\n重要犠牲幾多個手足，大家不如試下抖番幾日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1623283/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1623283/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n最新風向撚, 入去不推文回覆拉番落黎"},{"pid":"9942d26cbdc6f23852d350597dbe07234c8b1492","tid":1623373,"uid":96694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"432d16ed6de523b125dffcdf2dac346efb6eb71e","tid":1623373,"uid":89999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:40:06.000Z","msg":"最能癲既係你仲以為警察會同你講道理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:45:47.000Z","msg":"佢地唔講道理全港都知<br />\n但記者就係為左問出個真相 個真理出黎<br />\n記招佢地拎黎講大話<br />\n記者就追問到佢地啞為止<br />\n佢地總會有答唔出  輸既時候<br />\n輸人唔輸陣<br />\n佢地講幾多個大話<br />\n我地就揭穿返佢地咁多個大話<br />\n<br />\n相信咁多位前線記者啦<br />\n記者都一樣可以做到野架"},{"pid":"34931a32f96e65148b1d2e1f2c86ae7198df8192","tid":1623373,"uid":3162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:51:37.000Z","msg":"好想問有無其他地方嘅執法人員都係咁撚無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6901e7a6b925592d9ef59dc332afd8be9e075e59","tid":1623373,"uid":3162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:52:30.000Z","msg":"港共已經養撚到3萬隻狗唔記得左咩係良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c127230b66fa80baa749552662997b3ee8f4d76","tid":1623373,"uid":96694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34931a32f96e65148b1d2e1f2c86ae7198df8192","tid":1623373,"uid":3162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:51:37.000Z","msg":"好想問有無其他地方嘅執法人員都係咁撚無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\