 />\n<br />\n板機護環，trigger guard，用途係防止者誤觸板機誤射。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣警察未口頭警告，及未將手指放護環外，違反安全指引。加上警察仇視對方，失去專業判斷，多重犯錯下，致使對示威者胸口開槍，造成示威者重傷。<br />\n<br />\n高層完全曲解安全防禦法，唔怪得下屬都唔識，開槍殺人。警察上下都唔專業，點信班友持槍啊。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:48:07.000Z","msg":"屌係喎我打錯字<br />\n係 安全防禦法先岩...<br />\n明明check左  但唔記得改。"},{"pid":"005fdd7436e115b5b191124cd0ea440365ae2ccd","tid":1623373,"uid":96694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cd2ef2eddc5d79ee7cd5d9b92acc928f5fb8102","tid":1623373,"uid":8719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:18:49.000Z","msg":"留名聽日幫你再推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:48:58.000Z","msg":"然而我訓唔著  天光先再算啦"},{"pid":"5d0fcc146e051bc4eb2e13a692b42ebb1a0e711c","tid":1623373,"uid":96694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:49:29.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家早晨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9a2eeb59a24cba298753a4768a3c05f3c92597","tid":1623373,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:31:36.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"d29e403bc05a61a833f1acbb3a0a7d671d246a2c","tid":1623373,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}